            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Albior<supplied reason="lost">igi</supplied> <abbr>M</abbr> Servata <lb n="2"/>et suis <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aeta</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(a): Durchmesser: 10.4; (b): Höhe: 1.; Breite: 2 0.4; Durchmesser: 4.2 Quattro frammenti ricongiunti ed integrati di coppa troncoconica in sigillata gallica, forma Drag. 33.</p>
            </div>
